<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Reset OTP | Bighil</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap");

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          "Inter",
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI",
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #242e4c;
        background: #f7f9f8;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        padding: 20px 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow:
          0 20px 40px rgba(36, 46, 76, 0.08),
          0 8px 24px rgba(36, 46, 76, 0.04);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #f4fdf6;
        position: relative;
      }

      .email-wrapper::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 4px;
        background: #198754;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 40px 32px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        background: #f4fdf6;
        position: relative;
      }

      .header::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 80px;
        height: 2px;
        background: #198754;
        border-radius: 2px;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 140px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.1));
      }

      .brand-text {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #198754;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      .brand-subtitle {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6c757d;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 48px 32px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .security-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: #d1e7dd;
        color: #198754;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .security-badge::before {
        content: "üîí";
        margin-right: 8px;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #242e4c;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #242e4c;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .message {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #495057;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .otp-container {
        background: #198754;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .otp-container::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(
          circle,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%,
          transparent 70%
        );
        animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes shimmer {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(0deg);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(0%) translateY(0%) rotate(180deg);
        }
      }

      .otp-label {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 48px;
        letter-spacing: 12px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 20px 32px;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .otp-timer {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .timer-icon {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      .steps-container {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 32px 0;
        border: 1px solid #eff6f1;
      }

      .steps-title {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #242e4c;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        font-size: 18px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .steps-title::before {
        content: "üìù";
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .steps-list {
        list-style: none;
        counter-reset: step-counter;
      }

      .steps-list li {
        counter-increment: step-counter;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        padding-left: 0;
        color: #495057;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .steps-list li::before {
        content: counter(step-counter);
        background: #198754;
        color: white;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-right: 12px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .security-tips {
        background: #fff3cd;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .security-tips-title {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #663c00;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .security-tips-title::before {
        content: "‚ö°";
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .security-tips-list {
        list-style: none;
        color: #663c00;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .security-tips-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .security-tips-list li::before {
        content: "‚Ä¢";
        color: #ffc107;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-right: 8px;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .warning-section {
        background: #f8d7da;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .warning-title {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #721c24;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .warning-title::before {
        content: "‚ö†Ô∏è";
      }

      .warning-text {
        color: #721c24;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .help-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background: #cff4fc;
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .help-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #055160;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .help-text {
        color: #0c525d;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .support-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: #0dcaf0;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(13, 202, 240, 0.3);
      }

      .support-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(13, 202, 240, 0.4);
      }

      .support-link::before {
        content: "üí¨";
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }

      .social-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .social-link {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .social-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
      }

      .social-facebook {
        background: #4267b2;
        color: white;
      }

      .social-twitter {
        background: #1da1f2;
        color: white;
      }

      .social-linkedin {
        background: #0077b5;
        color: white;
      }

      .company-info {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6c757d;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .copyright {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #adb5bd;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #198754;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 0 12px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 32px 20px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 32px 20px 24px;
        }

        .title {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .otp-code {
          font-size: 36px;
          letter-spacing: 8px;
          padding: 16px 24px;
        }

        .otp-container {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .steps-container,
        .security-tips,
        .warning-section,
        .help-section {
          padding: 20px 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
          <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="Bighil Logo" class="logo" />
          <div class="brand-text">Bighil</div>
          <div class="brand-subtitle">Security First</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <div class="security-badge">Secure Authentication</div>

          <h1 class="title">Password Reset Request</h1>

          <p class="greeting">Hello <%= userName %>,</p>

          <p class="message">
            We've received a request to reset the password for your Bighil
            account. To ensure the security of your account, please use the
            one-time password below to complete the verification process.
          </p>

          <div class="otp-container">
            <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <div class="otp-timer">
              <svg class="timer-icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Expires in 2 minutes
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="steps-container">
            <h3 class="steps-title">Complete Your Password Reset</h3>
            <ol class="steps-list">
              <li>
                Enter the 6-digit verification code above in the password reset
                form
              </li>
              <li>Create a strong, unique password for your account</li>
              <li>Confirm your new password and save the changes</li>
              <li>Sign in with your new credentials to access your account</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="security-tips">
            <h3 class="security-tips-title">Security Best Practices</h3>
            <ul class="security-tips-list">
              <li>
                Never share your verification code with anyone, including Bighil
                support staff
              </li>
              <li>
                Use a unique password that contains uppercase, lowercase,
                numbers, and symbols
              </li>
              <li>
                Avoid using personal information or common words in your
                password
              </li>
              <li>
                Consider using a password manager to generate and store secure
                passwords
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="warning-section">
            <h3 class="warning-title">Didn't Request This?</h3>
            <p class="warning-text">
              If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email
              and consider changing your password immediately. Your account
              security is important to us.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="help-section">
            <h3 class="help-title">Need Help?</h3>
            <p class="help-text">Our support team is here to help you 24/7</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@bighil.com" class="support-link"
              >Contact Support</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p class="company-info">
            <strong>Bighil</strong><br />
            123 Business Avenue, Tech City 10001
          </p>

          <p class="copyright">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Bighil. All rights reserved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
